{
  "texts": [
    "In a second step, we counted the words indicative of GPT-4 and compared the frequency with which they occurred in both human and GPT-4 reappraisals.",
    "As expected based on the class-based TFIDF, we found those words more frequently in GPT-4 versus human reappraisals (see SI).",
    "We then correlated the use of indicative GPT-4 words with reappraisal quality for GPT and humans.",
    "We found that the frequency of words was positively associated with all quality indicators for humans, but not GPT in Studies 1 and 2 (Table 5).",
    "As a robustness check we correlated the frequency of words across studies (i.e., indicative words for GPT-4 from Study 1 in data from Studies 2 and 4, etc.)"
  ]
}